{"tid":785617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【做業主VS做租租】逾21%劏房女住客曾遭性騷擾   事主：被業主摸胸但不追究","createTime":"2018-08-19T10:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T17:19:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b764a1f370018097398fb5e343a7d9980b71d513","tid":785617,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:56:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180819/58582472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58582472&d=gTn8TklaZDEjTPqfaWz9jRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=204c6e35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58582472&h=8b60343c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180819/58582472</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180819/large/1534669414_6eff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180819%2Flarge%2F1534669414_6eff.png&h=30fb023d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWinnie曾被所住劏房的業主大力摸胸，但最終未有追究。<br />\n<br />\n香港土地問題嚴重，在狹窄空間居住的劏房女住客更有被性騷擾危機。關注基層住屋聯席公佈《女性於劏房內受到性騷擾情況》調查結果，受訪的105名女性劏房住戶當中，逾一成七受訪者（22人）表示曾遭不同程度的性騷擾，更有受害人多次遭性騷擾，最常見的是在單位內被言語調戲，其中4人更表示曾遭接觸或被摩擦身體，共有31.4%受訪者（33人）表示曾在單位內曾經歷性騷擾或感到不便。<br />\n<br />\n關注基層住屋聯席以問卷形式訪問105位居住九龍區（深水埗、九龍城、油尖旺、觀塘）、葵青區及灣仔區劏房的女住客，逾8成受訪者均為套房住客，平均居住呎數為115.8。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180819/large/1534669414_b7a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180819%2Flarge%2F1534669414_b7a0.png&h=b2556d66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾居住深水埗區劏房的Vivian指，自己住在分成3間相連房間的套房單位，每天下班返回房間時必須經過共用的走廊，而走廊第一間房的男住客常穿背心及「孖煙通」坐在房內，望著房門外，Vivian稱感「被監視」，「要急急腳咁衝返入房」。<br />\n<br />\n另一個案劏房女住戶Winnie更指自己曾被「業主用力咁摸咗個胸部」。她憶述事發時因房內無電視，來自不同房間的住客及業主，一同在客廳看電視，有一次業主突出手性騷擾，雖已即時嚴斥對方，對方有即時道歉，自己則返回房內，自此與業主再無交流，1年約滿後便搬離該處。<br />\n<br />\n組織幹事任真指，劏房租客多數只簽1年合約，流動性高，難免住客或良莠不齊，共用空間如走廊的燈光多數較昏暗，女住客心理長期受壓，擔心居家私人時間都會被性騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n律師莊耀洸指，因此類個案發生於劏房內，非公共空間少有目擊證人，難以搜證。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/02/104639_2ded5965f877a363f2885577ed7aa454.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2F104639_2ded5965f877a363f2885577ed7aa454.jpeg&h=cb4bfe0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03c90e33ae243cbfff76b19d76311af993ed8733","tid":785617,"uid":132587,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads//2014/08/10527571_10152536700607225_613556607023761615_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F%2F2014%2F08%2F10527571_10152536700607225_613556607023761615_n.jpg&h=9c48379f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f293586ed7b59f2be4a30e78170a169b5b30c538","tid":785617,"uid":11067,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:57:18.000Z","msg":"一次性交一次.jpg"},{"pid":"3950d15b5e8f863e9e6aa093e49a3935f7cf0d04","tid":785617,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}